 685:Libraries/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_i2c.c ****   *     @arg I2C_NACKPosition_Next: indicates that the next byte will be the last
 686:Libraries/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_i2c.c ****   *          received byte.  
 687:Libraries/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_i2c.c ****   *     @arg I2C_NACKPosition_Current: indicates that current byte is the last 
