1185:Libraries/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_i2c.c ****   *   This parameter can be any combination of the following values:
1186:Libraries/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_i2c.c ****   *     @arg I2C_FLAG_SMBALERT: SMBus Alert flag
1187:Libraries/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_i2c.c ****   *     @arg I2C_FLAG_TIMEOUT: Timeout or Tlow error flag
