1191:Libraries/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_i2c.c ****   *     @arg I2C_FLAG_ARLO: Arbitration lost flag (Master mode)
1192:Libraries/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_i2c.c ****   *     @arg I2C_FLAG_BERR: Bus error flag
