1198:Libraries/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_i2c.c ****   *   - ADD10 (10-bit header sent) is cleared by software sequence: a read 
1199:Libraries/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_i2c.c ****   *     operation to I2C_SR1 (I2C_GetFlagStatus()) followed by writing the 
