1201:Libraries/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_i2c.c ****   *   - BTF (Byte Transfer Finished) is cleared by software sequence: a read 
1202:Libraries/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_i2c.c ****   *     operation to I2C_SR1 register (I2C_GetFlagStatus()) followed by a 
1203:Libraries/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_i2c.c ****   *     read/write to I2C_DR register (I2C_SendData()).
1204:Libraries/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_i2c.c ****   *   - ADDR (Address sent) is cleared by software sequence: a read operation to 
1205:Libraries/STM32F10x_StdPeriph_Driver/src/stm32f10x_i2c.c ****   *     I2C_SR1 register (I2C_GetFlagStatus()) followed by a read operation to 
